title: Cottage in Ben Lomond
posting_body: ['This bright, sunny beautifully appointed detached cottage/loft in Ben Lomond is a rare find.', '  While just around 425 sq.', 'ft, it boasts a full kitchen with a dishwasher, an in unit washer/dryer combo, propane heat, a private deck, a small storage area and loads of sunshine and atmosphere.', 'Just 1 mile from Hwy 9, this unit is fully or partially furnished and suited for one person only (no exceptions).', 'WiFi and trash are included.', " Tenant pays propane, water and electricity (on it's own meter) Current tenant pays approx $125 per month with conscientious use.", 'Street parking.', 'Ideal tenant is very quiet, exceptionally tidy and financially stable.', ' There is no smoking of any sort on the property and no pets.', 'Rent $1875.', ' Deposit $3000.', 'One year lease.', 'Application: Please email me a little about yourself.', ' If we think its a fit, application will need to include:', '6 months bank statements', '3 months paystubs', 'Credit report', 'References of last landlord']
